{"tid":1248640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢個時候要人鏈","createTime":"2019-06-21T13:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T13:55:18.000Z","uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"34440fd100b3f04ea5f48ec547e6555960a26da3","tid":1248640,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:41:37.000Z","msg":"衝黎托咩"},{"pid":"7a83004f2faf9d4c2fdb0a9999b602deaccce35b","tid":1248640,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:43:44.000Z","msg":"泛民G峰民陣去曬邊？係時候需要你地出場"},{"pid":"6c917384f9bca1ac8fd99fc8a8a208a7978fd156","tid":1248640,"uid":79182,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:45:21.000Z","msg":"大家記住 呢個係長期不合作運動<br />\n我地淨係圍住佢 唔好衝<br />\n啲犬清場 我地唔使硬碰<br />\n唔好送人頭俾佢<br />\n我地返去休息 抖足精神 第二日又嚟過<br />\n我地不斷做 搞亂個社會秩序<br />\n然後同政府談判先係辦法<br />\n<br />\n千其唔好死衝 無意思㗎 <br />\n我地做咩都唔合法<br />\n警犬做咩都有政府撐腰<br />\n我真係唔想再有義士犧牲<br />\n<br />\n我知有人會諗 叫咗咁多人出嚟<br />\n咩都唔做咁on9?<br />\n無錯我地係人多 但我地和平遊行又試過<br />\n衝擊佔領又試過 有用咩??<br />\n要贏 一定要試新方法<br />\n一於試吓不合作運動啦"},{"pid":"319f2739b715221ced50426ce2daa771b1c32a8b","tid":1248640,"uid":261169,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:47:45.000Z","msg":"忍住啊大家"},{"pid":"1b275f7ab62cd5121402275b100bec151d966012","tid":1248640,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:48:36.000Z","msg":"支持 烈士遺言 我地唔係暴徒<br />\n<br />\n我地唔洗自眨身價同佢鬥賤架!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認清目標 聚焦醫警濫權<br />\n<br />\n修例係撤回定停止已經唔係重點<br />\n<br />\n今日圍完 應該盡早散 僵持不下無意思<br />\n<br />\n國際人權組織已經出左報告 今晚有意外就前功盡廢了<br />\n<br />\n手足辛苦完 應該到宣傳組出場<br />\n<br />\n多謝各位耐心睇完"},{"pid":"7ade909d2285e4048475e6c7a6ba78b0d9726ab2","tid":1248640,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:50:29.000Z","msg":"人鏈係攞黎防鬼，人唔驚最驚鬼"},{"pid":"f6cdcb3243eaa9bf2941fd7bdedd96c59f89bb77","tid":1248640,"uid":148987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:52:17.000Z","msg":"唔贊成衝<br />\n但人鏈係示弱象徵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪撚再重覆2014 個x Japan 唔該"},{"pid":"eff11e3cc40f37e9bb92d56a9a62646cbe8c69b1","tid":1248640,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6cdcb3243eaa9bf2941fd7bdedd96c59f89bb77","tid":1248640,"uid":148987,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:52:17.000Z","msg":"唔贊成衝<br />\n但人鏈係示弱象徵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪撚再重覆2014 個x Japan 唔該"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T13:55:18.000Z","msg":"手拖手就得，除左人鏈冇咩野防到鬼"}]}